Lightom

Lightom (Light On Management) is a project under GPLv3 about IoT
(Internet of Things).

# Python

* Requeriments
 - python >= 3.5.2
 - django >= 1.10.4

* Install
 - pyvenv .env
 - . .env/bin/activate
 - pip install requeriments

* Run
 - . .env/bin/activate
 - cd web
 - python manage.py runserver

Access localhost:8000/web

# Guile

* Requeriments
 - guile >= 2.0

* Install (Guix)
 `guix package -i artanis'

* Install (Debian/Trisquel)
 `sudo apt-get install guile-2.0-dev guile-2.0 artanis
wget -c http://alpha.gnu.org/gnu/artanis/artanis-latest.tar.bz2
tar xvjf artanis-latest.tar.bz2
cd artanis-latest && ./configure && make
sudo make install'

* Run
 - art work

Access localhost:3000

